metadata.name: #iBIZA01
metadata.description:
The photo was taken near the iconic cliff overlooking Mount Esvedra, rising out of the sea. If you climb up the hillside parallel to the cliff, you can see exactly the same view as in the picture. For those of you looking for the lost city of Atlantis, it can be seen in the bottom right corner.

*This work is part of a collection inspired by the idea of a world where big dreams are allowed! If you feel like you are different and you don't fit in, you can join the dreamers club by buying this artwork. 

*Each photo is unique and made by @iclickuwatch also known as @kristian_petrovcic_photography

*One Crypto @iclickuwatch token is your ticket to future drops, events, discounts for photo/video projects and much much more. Join the community today at foundation.app/@iclickuwatch
